even lead to bullying

00:02:40.994 --> 00:02:43.288
and discrimination
among the children.

00:02:43.330 --> 00:02:45.749
Plus, hazing from
the honor students.

00:02:45.791 --> 00:02:49.086
Tension between the dorm
kids and commuters, too.

00:02:49.127 --> 00:02:52.172
[sighs] Speaking of, I hear
lots of those commuters

00:02:52.214 --> 00:02:53.799
have been kidnapped lately.

00:02:53.840 --> 00:02:54.883
But it's no surprise,

00:02:54.925 --> 00:02:58.178
since most of the students
come from rich families.

00:02:58.220 --> 00:03:00.097
I don't wanna go
to school anymore.

00:03:00.138 --> 00:03:01.598
[TWILIGHT gasps]

00:03:01.640 --> 00:03:05.477
I'm sorry, dear.
I didn't mean to frighten you.

00:03:05.519 --> 00:03:08.814
Don't worry, there's plenty of
fun to be had at Eden, too.

00:03:08.855 --> 00:03:11.525
There, you're all measured.

00:03:11.566 --> 00:03:14.361
Okay, you're getting one
uniform, a winter coat,

00:03:14.403 --> 00:03:18.031
a vest, and a sweater, so that's
three additional items.

00:03:18.073 --> 00:03:18.949
Since you're a regular,

00:03:18.990 --> 00:03:21.451
I'll bump you up on
the priority list.

00:03:21.493 --> 00:03:23.829
Oh, and you'll be able to get
everything else you need

00:03:23.870 --> 00:03:25.789
from that shop on the corner.

00:03:25.831 --> 00:03:27.916
[TWILIGHT]
Getting pricey.

00:03:31.837 --> 00:03:33.380
[TWILIGHT]
Hm? What's wrong?

00:03:33.422 --> 00:03:35.549
I'm trying to not get kidnapped.

00:03:35.590 --> 00:03:38.719
[TWILIGHT]
I see. Interesting approach.

00:03:38.760 --> 00:03:41.722
Hey, Yor, is it all right
if we eat out today?

00:03:41.763 --> 00:03:43.515
[YOR]
Yes, of course.

00:03:43.557 --> 00:03:47.352
[ANYA] Are there any kidnappers
at the restaurant?

00:03:47.394 --> 00:03:48.937
[WAITER A]
Here's today's special.

00:03:48.979 --> 00:03:50.897
Pork sauté in a pawpaw sauce

00:03:50.939 --> 00:03:54.025
with porcini mushrooms
and potato potage.

00:03:54.067 --> 00:03:55.569
Enjoy.

00:03:55.610 --> 00:03:56.403
[ANYA]
Po?

00:03:56.445 --> 00:03:57.362
Looks great!

00:03:57.404 --> 00:04:00.824
[TWILIGHT] Cipher P, eh?
This is about my briefing.

00:04:00.866 --> 00:04:07.080
It's in five days at 1300 hours
at safe house D. Got it.

00:04:07.122 --> 00:04:09.958
But I should really ask them
to stop using this method.

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:12.794
It's unpleasant.

00:04:12.836 --> 00:04:15.464
[phone ringing]

00:04:15.505 --> 00:04:16.590
Hello?

00:04:16.631 --> 00:04:20.552
Yes, this is him.
Oh, it's done already?

00:04:20.594 --> 00:04:24.890
All right. We'll come pick
it up today. Thank you.

00:04:27.017 --> 00:04:29.269
So? Are my clothes done?

00:04:29.311 --> 00:04:31.605
Sounds like it.

00:04:31.646 --> 00:04:34.149
[TWILIGHT]
But I've got my briefing today.

00:04:34.191 --> 00:04:35.776
Sorry to throw this on you,

00:04:35.817 --> 00:04:38.195
but do you think you
could pick the order up?

00:04:38.236 --> 00:04:41.490
I would, but I have to work.

00:04:41.531 --> 00:04:44.284
No problem. You can count on me.

00:04:44.326 --> 00:04:46.453
[TWILIGHT] I might not get
home until pretty late,

00:04:46.495 --> 00:04:49.790
so you two can probably go
ahead and order in tonight.

00:04:49.831 --> 00:04:50.582
Sure.

00:04:50.624 --> 00:04:52.667
[ANYA]
Have a rice day!

00:05:03.136 --> 00:05:04.888
[doorbell rings]

00:05:25.242 --> 00:05:27.994
Good afternoon,
or rather, good evening.

00:05:28.036 --> 00:05:30.789
Nice to see you, Twilight.

00:05:30.831 --> 00:05:33.834
[TWILIGHT] Hello, Handler.
What's this about?

00:05:33.875 --> 00:05:36.503
Before we get into it...

00:05:36.545 --> 00:05:38.505
What were all those
expenses the other day?!

00:05:38.547 --> 00:05:41.216
A castle rental fee and
furniture for the whole place?

00:05:41.258 --> 00:05:43.301
Do you think we're made
out of money here?

00:05:43.343 --> 00:05:47.180
Here's a couple more of them.
Turns out school is expensive.

00:05:47.222 --> 00:05:49.975
You've got stones to hand
me new ones like that.

00:05:50.016 --> 00:05:51.935
I mean, they're all necessary.

00:05:51.977 --> 00:05:53.103
Fine.

00:05:53.144 --> 00:05:56.398
Anyway, let's review
your next steps.

00:05:56.439 --> 00:05:58.859
This'll be phase two
of Operation Strix.

00:05:58.900 --> 00:06:02.153
Though knowing you, I doubt
you need such a reminder.

00:06:02.195 --> 00:06:03.697
Thank you, but honestly,

00:06:03.738 --> 00:06:06.491
I'm feeling a bit
off my game lately.

00:06:06.533 --> 00:06:08.910
[HANDLER] Phase two requires
a social gathering.

00:06:08.952 --> 00:06:12.789
Before we talk nitty-gritty,
let's revisit how Eden works.

00:06:12.831 --> 00:06:17.460
There are about 2500 students,
ranging from ages 6 to 19,

00:06:17.502 --> 00:06:20.505
and the curriculum
covers all 13 years.

00:06:20.547 --> 00:06:22.465
Academics, sports, the arts.

00:06:22.507 --> 00:06:25.927
They offer a top-class
education in every field.

00:06:25.969 --> 00:06:28.263
The students who manage
to distinguish themselves

00:06:28.305 --> 00:06:30.015
amongst even their fellow elites

00:06:30.056 --> 00:06:33.059
join the honor program
as "Imperial Scholars."

00:06:33.101 --> 00:06:35.228
As it so happens,
the social gathering

00:06:35.270 --> 00:06:37.230
that Desmond regularly attends

00:06:37.272 --> 00:06:40.609
is only open to the families
of said Imperial Scholars.

00:06:40.650 --> 00:06:42.819
In order to gain this
honor program title,

00:06:42.861 --> 00:06:46.406
a student must earn eight merits
known as "Stella Stars."

00:06:46.448 --> 00:06:48.325
They're awarded for
exceptional grades

00:06:48.366 --> 00:06:51.119
and contributions to society.

00:06:51.161 --> 00:06:54.247
Which means, first off, you will
need to turn your daughter

00:06:54.289 --> 00:06:55.749
into an honor student.

00:06:55.790 --> 00:06:58.251
And if that necessitates
underhanded methods,

00:06:58.293 --> 00:06:59.544
then so be it.

00:06:59.586 --> 00:07:00.754
But be careful.

00:07:00.795 --> 00:07:03.506
Those with poor grades or
exhibiting bad behavior

00:07:03.548 --> 00:07:06.343
are given demerits,
called "Tonitrus Bolts."

00:07:06.384 --> 00:07:08.219
When a student receives
eight of these,

00:07:08.261 --> 00:07:11.932
they are immediately expelled.

00:07:11.973 --> 00:07:12.891
Now, let's work...

00:07:12.933 --> 00:07:15.852
[TWILIGHT]
That girl, an honor student?

00:07:15.894 --> 00:07:18.897
That sinking feeling returns.

00:07:22.943 --> 00:07:24.778
Do I look cute in my uniform?

00:07:24.819 --> 00:07:25.695
[YOR]
Very!

00:07:25.737 --> 00:07:29.074
In fact, we should go to
the portrait studio later!

00:07:31.159 --> 00:07:32.786
[ANYA]
Ta-da!

00:07:32.827 --> 00:07:34.245
Do I still look cute?

00:07:34.287 --> 00:07:36.581
[YOR] It's not going
away anytime soon!

00:07:36.623 --> 00:07:40.085
How many times are you gonna
