00:08:27.173 --> 00:08:31.011
[YOR] I know that we're
just a pretend family,

00:08:31.052 --> 00:08:37.392
but I still feel like I want
to be a better mother to her.

00:08:38.685 --> 00:08:41.354
[ANYA]
Mama!

00:08:41.396 --> 00:08:44.649
