00:09:20.518 --> 00:09:22.353
[YOR] I'm not sure what
I'm gonna make yet,

00:09:22.395 --> 00:09:25.440
but if I get some meat and
vegetables, I'll be covered.

00:09:25.482 --> 00:09:27.609
