with us for a sec.

00:09:45.585 --> 00:09:49.214
Once your maid pays up, we'll
let ya go, so just sit tight.

00:09:49.255 --> 00:09:51.049
[ANYA]
Bad guys!

00:09:51.091 --> 00:09:54.260
I hear lots of those commuters
have been kidnapped.

00:09:54.302 --> 00:09:56.304
[ANYA]
She was right!

00:09:59.307 --> 00:10:01.893
You know, these uniforms
go for a good price.

00:10:01.935 --> 00:10:05.730
