I've been watching
him from the moment

00:14:14.687 --> 00:14:17.607
I saw his name on the
list of applicants.

00:14:17.648 --> 00:14:19.942
If plan A, the Imperial
Scholar route,

00:14:19.984 --> 00:14:22.570
proves too difficult,
we'll go to plan B.

00:14:22.612 --> 00:14:25.740
I call it:
"The Friendship Scheme."

00:14:25.782 --> 00:14:29.202
Step one, get into his class
and become his friend.

00:14:29.243 --> 00:14:32.705
Step two, get invited to his
house, with Dad in tow.

00:14:32.747 --> 00:14:36.084
Step three, direct contact
with the target.

00:14:36.125 --> 00:14:38.044
It'll likely be
more complicated,

00:14:38.086 --> 00:14:39.837
but we should be prepared.

00:14:39.879 --> 00:14:42.215
[INSTRUCTOR A]
Anya Forger.

00:14:42.256 --> 00:14:44.008
It's your turn.

00:14:45.551 --> 00:14:47.595
[TWILIGHT] I'm sure Anya
grew up around a lot of kids

00:14:47.637 --> 00:14:50.556
during her days
at the orphanage.

00:14:50.598 --> 00:14:54.394
Gives me faith in her
communication skills.

00:14:54.435 --> 00:14:57.438
[ANYA]
That's the bad guy boss's kid.

00:14:57.480 --> 00:14:58.856
[DAMIAN]
What's her deal?

00:14:58.898 --> 00:15:01.109
Ha. I know.

00:15:01.150 --> 00:15:04.570
She took one look at me
and it was love at first sight.

00:15:04.612 --> 00:15:07.198
Well, she's got excellent taste.

00:15:08.491 --> 00:15:11.953
[DAMIAN]
Playing hard to get? How cute.

00:15:11.994 --> 00:15:14.664
[INSTRUCTOR A]
Becky Blackbell.

00:15:14.705 --> 00:15:17.291
[BECKY]
Nice to meet you!

00:15:17.333 --> 00:15:19.293
[TWILIGHT]
Hmm... Blackbell?

00:15:19.335 --> 00:15:22.755
Must be the daughter of that
major military contractor's CEO.

00:15:22.797 --> 00:15:26.217
Wait, and that girl's father
is the VP of parliament.

00:15:26.259 --> 00:15:29.095
And there's the son of a
prominent secret service member.

00:15:29.137 --> 00:15:31.973
Her classmates are a
treasure trove of intel!

00:15:32.014 --> 00:15:34.100
Anya better be friends
with all of them!

00:15:34.142 --> 00:15:35.685
[YOR giggles]

00:15:35.726 --> 00:15:38.187
[YOR] Loid gets so intense
when it comes to Anya!

00:15:38.229 --> 00:15:40.857
My name's Becky! What's yours?

00:15:40.898 --> 00:15:42.733
[BECKY]
She looks like a baby.

00:15:42.775 --> 00:15:44.652
I don't mind showin'
her the ropes.

00:15:44.694 --> 00:15:45.945
[ANYA gasps]

00:15:45.987 --> 00:15:47.071
[INSTRUCTOR A]
These 29 students...

00:15:47.113 --> 00:15:48.990
[TWILIGHT]
Don't be rude!

00:15:49.031 --> 00:15:50.241
[INSTRUCTOR A]
And will be under the tutelage

00:15:50.283 --> 00:15:52.827
of Master Henderson.

00:15:52.869 --> 00:15:54.829
Look! It's the nice one.

00:15:54.871 --> 00:15:56.956
[TWILIGHT]
Seems he kept his job.

00:15:56.998 --> 00:15:58.749
It's a bit unfair
for a housemaster

00:15:58.791 --> 00:16:00.710
to have to teach new students,

00:16:00.751 --> 00:16:03.337
but I suppose it
could've been worse.

00:16:03.379 --> 00:16:05.173
[HENDERSON] I'll whip these
rugrats into shape

00:16:05.214 --> 00:16:06.466
like the old days.

00:16:06.507 --> 00:16:07.925
[ANYA gasps]

00:16:07.967 --> 00:16:09.010
[INSTRUCTOR A]
And now, the new students

00:16:09.051 --> 00:16:11.596
will accompany their teachers
on a tour of the campus,

00:16:11.637 --> 00:16:14.348
then head to their
respective classrooms.

00:16:14.390 --> 00:16:16.392
While they are getting
acquainted with the grounds,

00:16:16.434 --> 00:16:18.060
all the parents are
cordially invited

00:16:18.102 --> 00:16:21.272
to get acquainted with each
other in the lounge of Tower C.

00:16:21.314 --> 00:16:23.774
[TWILIGHT] You'll be on your
own from here on out, Anya,

00:16:23.816 --> 00:16:26.569
so please, do your best.

00:16:27.695 --> 00:16:29.071
[ANYA]
Okey-dokey!

00:16:29.113 --> 00:16:31.240
[HENDERSON]
Forger! Stay in line!

00:16:31.282 --> 00:16:32.116
[BECKY giggles]

00:16:32.158 --> 00:16:34.160
Starting to worry.

00:16:34.202 --> 00:16:38.247
It's hard to send her off
into the world. She'll be okay.

00:16:41.250 --> 00:16:42.960
[HENDERSON]
This is the dining hall.

00:16:43.002 --> 00:16:45.129
You will be provided
the most elegant dishes

00:16:45.171 --> 00:16:47.381
made by world-class chefs.

00:16:47.423 --> 00:16:50.301
A special dining hall reserved
for Imperial Scholars

00:16:50.343 --> 00:16:52.553
lies just beyond those doors.

00:16:52.595 --> 00:16:55.515
Exhibit elegance in your
behavior and grades to receive

00:16:55.556 --> 00:16:58.768
the eight Stella required to
become an Imperial Scholar.

00:16:58.809 --> 00:17:00.978
So you must all
do your very best.

00:17:01.020 --> 00:17:02.355
[CHILDREN]
Sir!

00:17:02.396 --> 00:17:03.814
[HENDERSON]
However, be aware that those

00:17:03.856 --> 00:17:06.192
who miss the mark will
receive Tonitrus Bolts

00:17:06.234 --> 00:17:08.444
and face punishment
or expulsion.

00:17:08.486 --> 00:17:10.279
[ANYA]
Why's he looking at me?

00:17:10.321 --> 00:17:13.491
Lord Damian's gonna be an
Imperial Scholar in no time!

00:17:13.533 --> 00:17:14.784
I'm counting on it.

00:17:14.825 --> 00:17:16.410
You're in, for sure!

00:17:16.452 --> 00:17:19.580
I mean, my father is the head
of the National Unity Party.

00:17:19.622 --> 00:17:20.915
--Wait, seriously?
--[BOY B] Wow!

00:17:20.957 --> 00:17:22.750
[GIRL A] Oh! Father says
we owe quite a bit

00:17:22.792 --> 00:17:24.001
to the Desmond Group!

00:17:24.043 --> 00:17:26.504
[HENDERSON]
Silence! No private chatting!

00:17:26.546 --> 00:17:28.422
They're so dumb.

00:17:29.382 --> 00:17:31.050
[DAMIAN]
Hm.

00:17:31.092 --> 00:17:32.593
And what about you?

00:17:32.635 --> 00:17:34.428
What exactly does
your father do?

00:17:34.470 --> 00:17:35.346
If he's important,

00:17:35.388 --> 00:17:38.766
you might just have a chance
at being my friend.

00:17:38.808 --> 00:17:41.227
[ANYA]
Gotta stay cool for the mission.

00:17:41.269 --> 00:17:43.813
A sp-- He's a feelings doctor.

00:17:43.854 --> 00:17:44.855
[DAMIAN]
Hm.

00:17:44.897 --> 00:17:46.607
Sounds like a nobody to me.

00:17:46.649 --> 00:17:49.819
You're probably not very
rich, either. Pathetic.

00:17:49.860 --> 00:17:51.737
[ANYA]
I wanna go play at your house!

00:17:51.779 --> 00:17:54.699
No way! Why would he
want you there, ugly?

00:17:54.740 --> 00:17:56.867
These little peasants
are getting too bold!

00:17:56.909 --> 00:18:00.079
We don't want your grody
peasant germs, loser!

00:18:01.122 --> 00:18:04.041
[ANYA] Now is the time for me
to unleash my killer punch!

00:18:04.083 --> 00:18:06.294
[YOR]
Listen carefully, Anya.

00:18:06.335 --> 00:18:09.046
Anyone who lets their emotions
control their fists

00:18:09.088 --> 00:18:11.299
doesn't know the meaning
of true strength.

00:18:11.340 --> 00:18:13.050
If someone's being
a little rude,

00:18:13.092 --> 00:18:16.220
laughing it off makes you
the bigger, cooler girl.

00:18:16.262 --> 00:18:17.346
I'll be cool!

00:18:17.388 --> 00:18:19.098
[YOR] A smile can be
the strongest defense

00:18:19.140 --> 00:18:21.517
against any kind of
trouble or fight.

00:18:21.559 --> 00:18:23.269
Don't just stand
there and take it!

00:18:23.311 --> 00:18:25.688
At least call him
dumb or something.

00:18:25.730 --> 00:18:26.314
[ANYA]
Heh.

00:18:26.355 --> 00:18:28.524
I don't care what
you have to say.

00:18:28.566 --> 00:18:29.984
[DAMIAN]
Huh?

00:18:31.360 --> 00:18:32.987
[ANYA]
Heh.

00:18:33.029 --> 00:18:34.614
[DAMIAN]
What's with that smirk?

00:18:34.655 --> 00:18:37.158
How dare she mock me like this!

00:18:37.199 --> 00:18:38.951
[BECKY]
Look at that composure!

00:18:38.993 --> 00:18:42.913
She's not a baby after all.
She's cool and mature!

00:18:42.955 --> 00:18:43.914
[BECKY]
Wow!

00:18:43.956 --> 00:18:46.250
I'm super impressed at
how grown up you are!

00:18:46.292 --> 00:18:49.045
I'm a grown-up?

00:18:49.086 --> 00:18:50.880
[gasps]

00:18:52.048 --> 00:18:52.673
[ANYA]
Heh.

00:18:52.715 --> 00:18:55.009
[DAMIAN grunting]

00:18:55.051 --> 00:18:58.471
[DAMIAN] Don't get cocky,
you dumb ugly... uggo!

00:18:58.512 --> 00:19:01.891
Lord Damian, please
broaden your vocabulary.

00:19:01.932 --> 00:19:02.767
For real?

00:19:02.808 --> 00:19:04.185
She may be uglier than me,

00:19:04.226 --> 00:19:06.145
but you don't have to
be so rude about it.

00:19:06.187 --> 00:19:07.521
[DAMIAN]
Shut up!

00:19:07.563 --> 00:19:09.815
You! Must I repeat myself?

00:19:09.857 --> 00:19:12.526
You can be punished
on your first day!

00:19:12.568 --> 00:19:15.488
[DAMIAN] You brat. You'll pay
for embarrassing me.

00:19:15.529 --> 00:19:17.365
Watch your back!

00:19:17.406 --> 00:19:21.369
[ANYA] Mama's a liar.
Smiling didn't help one bit.

00:19:26.248 --> 00:19:28.376
--[DAMIAN whistling]
--[EWEN, EMILE chuckling]

00:19:28.417 --> 00:19:31.587
If you don't stop it right now,
I'm gonna tell the teacher!

00:19:31.629 --> 00:19:33.714
There's no proof
that we did anything.

00:19:33.756 --> 00:19:35.424
[EWEN, EMILE]
Nope, no proof!

00:19:35.466 --> 00:19:37.843
Just get outta my way.

00:19:37.885 --> 00:19:40.137
Listen, uggo!

00:19:40.179 --> 00:19:43.599
Every day I'll make it
my mission to bully you.

00:19:43.641 --> 00:19:44.767
When I'm through with you,

00:19:44.809 --> 00:19:47.311
you're never gonna
smirk like that again.

00:19:47.353 --> 00:19:49.897
If she cries, maybe her
"feelings doctor" daddy

00:19:49.939 --> 00:19:50.731
can fix her!

00:19:50.773 --> 00:19:53.734
[DAMIAN]
Ha! That's a good one!

00:19:53.776 --> 00:19:55.486
Daddy's widdle baby!

00:19:55.528 --> 00:19:57.905
[BOYS laughing]

00:19:57.947 --> 00:20:01.409
Hey, look at me, uggo!
Or are you scared?

00:20:01.450 --> 00:20:02.743
Huh?

00:20:12.878 --> 00:20:14.004
[HENDERSON]
What's going on?

00:20:14.046 --> 00:20:17.133
Teacher! This girl just
punched Lord Damian, sir!

00:20:17.174 --> 00:20:18.092
[ANYA gasps]

00:20:18.134 --> 00:20:20.428
I stuck out my hand
and he just ran into it.

00:20:20.469 --> 00:20:23.639
Don't lie! No one would ever
believe that stupid story!

00:20:23.681 --> 00:20:25.933
Yeah! You even made sure
the teacher wasn't looking

00:20:25.975 --> 00:20:26.976
before you hit him!

00:20:27.017 --> 00:20:29.103
There's no proof
that I did anything.

00:20:29.186 --> 00:20:30.479
We can all see your fist mark

00:20:30.521 --> 00:20:32.982
right there on his
face, you know?

00:20:33.023 --> 00:20:36.694
Surely you're aware lying
is extremely inelegant.

00:20:36.736 --> 00:20:39.321
Anya Forger.

00:20:39.363 --> 00:20:41.365
[BECKY] But, sir,
that's not what happened.

00:20:41.407 --> 00:20:45.953
She was holding back all day,
but these bullies went too far.

00:20:45.995 --> 00:20:48.205
[HENDERSON]
So it's true that you hit him?

00:20:48.247 --> 00:20:50.249
[grunts]

00:20:50.291 --> 00:20:52.710
[YOR]
This is very important, Anya.

00:20:52.752 --> 00:20:54.879
Never use force, okay?

00:20:54.920 --> 00:20:56.130
Unless it's, like,

00:20:56.172 --> 00:20:59.842
a situation where you have
to save a friend in trouble.

00:21:01.343 --> 00:21:04.680
[ANYA]
I-I was saving her.

00:21:04.722 --> 00:21:09.435
He stepped on her foot,
and that made me really angry.

00:21:09.477 --> 00:21:11.103
I'm so sorry.

00:21:11.145 --> 00:21:12.688
[BECKY gasps]

00:21:12.730 --> 00:21:17.526
[BECKY] She did that
for me? How sweet!

00:21:17.568 --> 00:21:21.113
[HENDERSON] She showed restraint
in regards to her own abuse,

00:21:21.155 --> 00:21:24.575
as well as the courage to
defend a friend in need.

00:21:24.617 --> 00:21:30.289
Truly elegant, Anya Forger.
However, I'm afraid...

00:21:30.331 --> 00:21:34.168
[TWILIGHT] It seems the Desmonds
never even showed up.

00:21:34.210 --> 00:21:36.712
Well, no need to rush things.

00:21:36.754 --> 00:21:40.007
Now that she's enrolled at
Eden, we have ample time.

00:21:40.049 --> 00:21:42.009
And I was able to make
a few connections.

00:21:42.051 --> 00:21:44.553
...please head toward the
courtyard to greet them.

00:21:44.595 --> 00:21:46.931
Now gather round so we can
take our group photo.

00:21:46.972 --> 00:21:48.349
Where's Anya?

00:21:48.390 --> 00:21:50.768
[HENDERSON]
Forger, a moment.

00:21:51.852 --> 00:21:54.271
[TWILIGHT]
She punched a boy?

00:21:54.313 --> 00:21:55.189
He didn't hurt you, did he?

00:21:55.231 --> 00:21:58.317
[TWILIGHT] And of course,
it had to be Desmonds' son.

00:21:58.359 --> 00:21:59.151
Who else?

00:21:59.193 --> 00:22:01.237
...would result in three
Tonitrus Bolts.

00:22:01.278 --> 00:22:03.989
But it became one,
with my discretion.

00:22:04.031 --> 00:22:07.117
That was truly the
best I could do.

00:22:07.159 --> 00:22:08.953
I am so sorry, Loid!

00:22:08.994 --> 00:22:11.121
I think it's because of
the way I trained her.

00:22:11.163 --> 00:22:11.914
And of course,

00:22:11.956 --> 00:22:15.125
I'll have to have a word
with his parents as well.

00:22:15.167 --> 00:22:16.418
[TWILIGHT]
It's the first day of school

00:22:16.460 --> 00:22:18.546
and she's already lost a point.

00:22:18.587 --> 00:22:22.758
And her relationship with Damian
may prove unsalvageable.

00:22:22.800 --> 00:22:25.427
All right, everyone,
we're almost ready!

00:22:25.469 --> 00:22:27.096
Now, the family on
the right over there?

00:22:27.137 --> 00:22:30.724
I need you to smile!
Say, "Cheese"!

00:24:16.622 --> 00:24:18.624
[inaudible]

